WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:02.980
[2025 Chungnam location incentive
production support project]

00:00:11.030 --> 00:00:13.500
[Woo Jihan]

00:00:15.760 --> 00:00:18.340
[Shin Jeongyou]

00:00:20.320 --> 00:00:22.600
[Min Dohee]

00:00:24.100 --> 00:00:26.680
[Seo Seunghyeon]

00:00:30.620 --> 00:00:35.020
[Always Meet Again]

00:00:38.220 --> 00:00:39.100
Eunha!

00:00:41.460 --> 00:00:43.060
Woojin went to the hospital?

00:00:43.130 --> 00:00:44.130
Woojin?

00:00:44.310 --> 00:00:45.310
Oh, him.

00:00:46.490 --> 00:00:48.110
You were together last time too.

00:00:48.110 --> 00:00:49.910
Looks like you've gotten close.

00:00:50.410 --> 00:00:51.540
Is he badly injured?

00:00:53.290 --> 00:00:55.480
I just asked him to go take an x-ray.

00:00:55.510 --> 00:00:56.640
He broke something?

00:00:57.630 --> 00:00:58.200
Hey.

00:00:58.270 --> 00:01:00.580
It's normal for boys
to get hurt while playing basketball.

00:01:00.580 --> 00:01:01.950
Why are you so shocked?

00:01:02.410 --> 00:01:03.330
They'll contact me soon,

00:01:03.330 --> 00:01:04.660
so don't worry too much.

00:01:10.260 --> 00:01:11.920
Might as well go to this place.

00:01:12.720 --> 00:01:14.870
[Art Room]

00:01:14.870 --> 00:01:16.820
Give it back before the break ends.

00:01:19.039 --> 00:01:20.100
Are you telling me to go now?

00:01:20.100 --> 00:01:20.690
Yes.

00:01:20.830 --> 00:01:22.960
I have to return it as soon as possible.

00:01:26.780 --> 00:01:28.920
[Art Room]

00:02:08.430 --> 00:02:12.780
[Episode 3:
Feelings That Can't Be Suppressed]

00:02:23.430 --> 00:02:24.780
If nothing changes...

00:02:25.660 --> 00:02:27.120
No—if it can't be changed,

00:02:28.590 --> 00:02:30.050
it's better to leave here.

00:03:07.890 --> 00:03:08.720
What's going on?

00:03:08.720 --> 00:03:10.050
Why is it still the same?

00:03:11.380 --> 00:03:11.850
Hey.

00:03:12.340 --> 00:03:14.290
I drew the same thing as I did last time.

00:03:14.290 --> 00:03:15.290
What's wrong?

00:03:23.610 --> 00:03:24.610
Hey, sketchbook.

00:03:24.870 --> 00:03:25.870
Let me back.

00:03:30.180 --> 00:03:31.110
What's going on?

00:03:31.340 --> 00:03:32.600
This doesn't work too?

00:03:33.930 --> 00:03:34.930
Hey, you...

00:03:35.730 --> 00:03:37.190
Is it because it's not complete?

00:03:37.190 --> 00:03:37.650
Okay.

00:03:51.740 --> 00:03:53.000
That's enough, right?

00:04:04.390 --> 00:04:05.390
What's going on?

00:04:05.580 --> 00:04:06.840
This doesn't work too?

00:04:06.910 --> 00:04:08.860
What am I supposed to do? Gah!

00:04:37.290 --> 00:04:38.420
Hey, Jang Hyeseong.

00:04:39.530 --> 00:04:41.790
Woojin is in the hospital
because of you.

00:04:43.130 --> 00:04:43.990
I know.

00:04:47.440 --> 00:04:49.050
Be careful next time.

00:04:49.560 --> 00:04:51.690
You got into trouble on your first day.

00:04:51.720 --> 00:04:52.860
Because of you, the class teacher

00:04:52.860 --> 00:04:54.590
calls me over every break time.

00:04:56.070 --> 00:04:57.070
I'm sorry.

00:04:59.620 --> 00:05:00.620
Also,

00:05:01.850 --> 00:05:04.380
it seems like
you're getting close to Woojin.

00:05:07.390 --> 00:05:08.650
He's my best friend...

00:05:14.340 --> 00:05:15.600
So let's get close too.

00:05:18.300 --> 00:05:19.020
Oh...

00:05:19.020 --> 00:05:19.870
Sure.

00:05:20.000 --> 00:05:21.280
Okay!

00:05:21.650 --> 00:05:22.850
This is great, right?

00:05:24.230 --> 00:05:24.750
Gosh.

00:05:24.940 --> 00:05:26.210
That's so unc of you.

00:05:26.240 --> 00:05:27.190
Unc?

00:05:27.800 --> 00:05:28.930
What does that mean?

00:05:29.120 --> 00:05:29.690
Well...

00:05:29.810 --> 00:05:30.810
Nothing.

00:05:30.990 --> 00:05:32.880
It's something
you probably don't understand.

00:05:32.880 --> 00:05:34.940
There's nothing I don't understand.

00:05:35.580 --> 00:05:36.780
Let's say you do then.

00:05:37.480 --> 00:05:38.650
I just want to be alone now.

00:05:38.650 --> 00:05:39.909
Can you leave me alone?

00:05:40.130 --> 00:05:41.610
Gosh. What's wrong?

00:05:42.560 --> 00:05:43.990
Is something bothering you?

00:05:43.990 --> 00:05:45.790
Then consult me.

00:05:46.050 --> 00:05:46.620
Tell me.

00:05:46.630 --> 00:05:47.850
I can take care of everything.

00:05:47.850 --> 00:05:49.310
I said I wanted to be alone.

00:05:49.320 --> 00:05:50.180
Hey.

00:05:50.420 --> 00:05:52.590
Actually, you want to
get close to me too, right?

00:05:52.590 --> 00:05:53.320
I understand.

00:05:53.320 --> 00:05:53.650
No.

00:05:53.700 --> 00:05:55.280
What do you understand?

00:05:56.680 --> 00:05:58.640
You haven't changed at all.

00:05:59.080 --> 00:06:00.330
Of course I understand.

00:06:00.330 --> 00:06:02.090
You can't tell me that directly,

00:06:02.090 --> 00:06:03.980
so you're putting it in a vague way.

00:06:03.980 --> 00:06:04.580
All right.

00:06:04.850 --> 00:06:05.850
Let's go

00:06:06.030 --> 00:06:07.260
to the snack shop now.

00:06:07.600 --> 00:06:09.510
Let's go get a can of coke

00:06:09.520 --> 00:06:10.760
and have a deep chat.

00:06:11.430 --> 00:06:13.130
I don't want to become your friend,

00:06:13.130 --> 00:06:13.940
Taejun.

00:06:13.940 --> 00:06:15.210
You two seem close now.

00:06:18.700 --> 00:06:19.380
Woojin!

00:06:19.400 --> 00:06:20.520
Hey, are you okay?

00:06:20.630 --> 00:06:21.630
Are you okay?

00:06:22.860 --> 00:06:23.990
You have a fracture?

00:06:25.170 --> 00:06:26.570
It's just a minor injury.

00:06:27.630 --> 00:06:29.600
I wanted to take this opportunity

00:06:29.950 --> 00:06:31.420
so I asked the doctor
to give me a plaster.

00:06:31.420 --> 00:06:32.820
I'll be fine in a few days.

00:06:34.290 --> 00:06:35.880
I'm sorry. It's all my fault.

00:06:35.880 --> 00:06:37.250
No, it's not your fault.

00:06:37.500 --> 00:06:38.960
I was being unreasonable.

00:06:39.080 --> 00:06:40.140
No, it's my fault.

00:06:46.440 --> 00:06:47.440
If you feel sorry,

00:06:48.300 --> 00:06:49.840
buy me something from the snack shop.

00:06:49.840 --> 00:06:51.370
A patient needs nutrition.

00:06:52.010 --> 00:06:54.159
Buy whatever you want.

00:06:54.900 --> 00:06:55.900
Whatever I want?

00:06:56.330 --> 00:06:56.950
Yeah.

00:06:57.740 --> 00:06:58.520
Sure.

00:06:58.790 --> 00:06:59.990
I eat a lot.

00:07:01.740 --> 00:07:02.390
Let's go.

00:07:04.870 --> 00:07:05.870
Hey! Hey!

00:07:05.890 --> 00:07:06.920
Weren't we going to the snack shop?

00:07:06.920 --> 00:07:07.980
Let's go together!

00:07:22.780 --> 00:07:25.240
There's a reason
why you're so bad at sports.

00:07:25.910 --> 00:07:26.510
Huh?

00:07:26.740 --> 00:07:28.470
You're so talented in drawing.

00:07:28.930 --> 00:07:31.330
There's no need
for you to be good at sports.

00:07:31.900 --> 00:07:33.159
You're exaggerating.

00:07:33.920 --> 00:07:35.870
Hey, just major in art.

00:07:36.570 --> 00:07:37.990
I'm hopeless.

00:07:40.360 --> 00:07:41.560
Just draw something.

00:07:42.520 --> 00:07:44.320
I only know how to draw stickmen.

00:07:46.810 --> 00:07:48.010
Then just draw those.

00:07:48.110 --> 00:07:49.610
That's...

00:07:52.040 --> 00:07:53.810
Is there anything you want to draw?

00:07:53.810 --> 00:07:55.740
Fill your drawing paper with that.

00:07:57.340 --> 00:07:58.530
What I want to draw?

00:08:01.790 --> 00:08:02.650
I got it—

00:08:03.190 --> 00:08:04.300
what I want to draw.

00:08:17.480 --> 00:08:20.130
All right, did you practice well today?

00:08:20.820 --> 00:08:22.340
Before the next class,

00:08:22.370 --> 00:08:25.170
hand in your sketchbook
with what you want to draw.

00:08:25.280 --> 00:08:27.540
For the theme—like I mentioned just now—

00:08:27.670 --> 00:08:28.530
it's freestyle.

00:08:28.530 --> 00:08:29.570
So,

00:08:29.600 --> 00:08:32.070
I don't want to see how technical
your drawing is,

00:08:32.070 --> 00:08:33.450
but how much sincerity

00:08:33.470 --> 00:08:35.000
you put into your painting.

00:08:35.799 --> 00:08:36.799
Don't think too much.

00:08:36.799 --> 00:08:38.200
No need to feel stressed.

00:08:39.340 --> 00:08:40.299
Sir.

00:08:40.320 --> 00:08:42.030
You're making us feel more stressed.

00:08:42.030 --> 00:08:43.539
Just give us a theme.

00:08:43.570 --> 00:08:44.810
This is too difficult.

00:08:44.810 --> 00:08:45.720
Nah, nah.

00:08:45.740 --> 00:08:46.800
You're doing well.

00:08:46.990 --> 00:08:48.610
That's all for today.

00:08:48.810 --> 00:08:49.810
See you next time.

00:08:49.920 --> 00:08:50.920
-Okay.
-Okay.

00:08:56.670 --> 00:08:58.130
I've decided on the theme.

00:08:59.010 --> 00:08:59.650
What is it?

00:08:59.740 --> 00:09:02.120
But I don't know how to draw it yet.

00:09:03.110 --> 00:09:04.620
So I need your help.

00:09:06.780 --> 00:09:07.600
Me?

00:09:07.800 --> 00:09:09.730
By the riverside we went to last time.

00:09:09.730 --> 00:09:11.710
I taught you how to play basketball.

00:09:11.710 --> 00:09:13.640
It's only fair to return the favor.

00:09:15.520 --> 00:09:16.410
What—

00:09:16.780 --> 00:09:18.040
You'll help me, right?

00:09:32.020 --> 00:09:33.020
Oh!

00:09:34.620 --> 00:09:35.900
You looked so reluctant,

00:09:35.900 --> 00:09:38.230
but it looks like you came well-prepared.

00:09:38.470 --> 00:09:40.070
I don't know how to teach you.

00:09:40.380 --> 00:09:42.680
So I hope you can get inspiration
from nature.

00:09:42.680 --> 00:09:44.210
I don't want to draw nature.

00:09:44.240 --> 00:09:45.270
I want to draw a portrait.

00:09:45.270 --> 00:09:45.590
Hey.

00:09:45.620 --> 00:09:47.510
It's hard for a beginner
to draw portraits.

00:09:47.510 --> 00:09:49.630
That's why I'm asking you to teach me.

00:09:51.380 --> 00:09:52.380
Fine.

00:09:52.960 --> 00:09:53.810
Who do you want to draw?

00:09:53.810 --> 00:09:55.080
It should be easier to draw

00:09:55.080 --> 00:09:57.080
if you have their characteristics.

00:09:59.780 --> 00:10:01.350
Let me see
if there are any characteristics.

00:10:01.350 --> 00:10:02.350
I just like to

00:10:03.260 --> 00:10:04.260
look at you.

00:10:07.420 --> 00:10:09.880
What characteristics
do you think you have?

00:10:12.020 --> 00:10:12.810
Me?

00:10:13.640 --> 00:10:14.700
You want to draw me?

00:10:15.700 --> 00:10:16.350
Mmhmm.

00:10:16.760 --> 00:10:17.820
You're my subject.

00:10:19.920 --> 00:10:21.920
But I'm going to draw a stickman
for your body.

00:10:21.920 --> 00:10:24.380
Just drawing your face would be
hard enough.

00:10:29.480 --> 00:10:30.480
Sure, I guess.

00:10:31.230 --> 00:10:32.490
It's up to the painter.

00:10:36.710 --> 00:10:37.550
Okay.

00:10:38.880 --> 00:10:39.390
I'm going to

00:10:39.390 --> 00:10:41.270
draw according to what I feel,

00:10:41.760 --> 00:10:43.690
then you give me some suggestions.

00:10:45.400 --> 00:10:46.400
Hey, hey!

00:10:46.880 --> 00:10:49.020
You should start sketching with a pencil.

00:10:49.020 --> 00:10:50.400
I want to paint the background first.

00:10:50.400 --> 00:10:51.860
Then the level of completion—

00:10:51.860 --> 00:10:53.830
The teacher said he wanted
to see our sincerity

00:10:53.830 --> 00:10:55.830
instead of the level of completion.

00:10:57.750 --> 00:10:58.430
Fine.

00:10:58.440 --> 00:10:59.370
Do what you want.

00:11:03.840 --> 00:11:04.840
Speaking of,

00:11:05.380 --> 00:11:06.580
what are you drawing?

00:11:07.690 --> 00:11:09.010
Well, I...

00:11:12.580 --> 00:11:15.200
-If you don't know, start with the background.
-Hey!

00:11:15.200 --> 00:11:17.020
I haven't decided on what to draw yet.

00:11:17.020 --> 00:11:18.880
Don't think too much.

00:11:19.340 --> 00:11:20.870
Just decide while drawing.

00:11:23.020 --> 00:11:24.560
You're really...

00:11:27.260 --> 00:11:28.260
But...

00:11:30.420 --> 00:11:31.770
-Don't you think this color is better?
-Hey!

00:11:31.770 --> 00:11:33.600
Just draw your own!

00:11:33.740 --> 00:11:35.870
What's yours and mine between us?

00:11:35.900 --> 00:11:37.680
If we draw together,
we can help each other—that's nice.

00:11:37.680 --> 00:11:39.130
You call that helping?

00:11:39.320 --> 00:11:40.000
Mmhmm.

00:11:40.250 --> 00:11:41.250
Is that so?

00:11:41.580 --> 00:11:42.440
Well, then...

00:11:42.700 --> 00:11:43.700
Why?

00:11:44.080 --> 00:11:45.080
Hey.

00:11:45.870 --> 00:11:46.850
I'll help you too!

00:11:46.850 --> 00:11:47.670
Hey!

00:11:50.330 --> 00:11:51.330
It's ruined!

00:11:53.990 --> 00:11:54.880
Stop it!

00:11:54.890 --> 00:11:55.890
Stop it!

00:11:56.300 --> 00:11:57.300
Stop it!

00:11:57.430 --> 00:11:58.630
It's ruined for real!

00:12:01.850 --> 00:12:03.910
Hey, are you sure it can be washed off?

00:12:04.180 --> 00:12:04.760
Yeah.

00:12:08.210 --> 00:12:09.610
Hey, it's not coming off.

00:12:10.190 --> 00:12:11.280
It comes off.

00:12:12.160 --> 00:12:12.830
Really?

00:12:12.990 --> 00:12:13.440
Yeah.

00:12:17.660 --> 00:12:18.660
Hey!

00:12:19.110 --> 00:12:20.110
What was that!

00:12:20.130 --> 00:12:20.830
Gosh!

00:12:20.850 --> 00:12:21.980
It's not coming off.

00:12:22.940 --> 00:12:23.740
Do you need my help?

00:12:23.740 --> 00:12:24.940
Is that enough water?

00:12:24.940 --> 00:12:26.080
Hey, don't do it.

00:12:26.360 --> 00:12:27.360
Don't!

00:12:28.630 --> 00:12:29.750
Hey, the water...

00:12:33.650 --> 00:12:34.650
Hey!

00:12:35.520 --> 00:12:36.440
Stop it!

00:12:54.580 --> 00:12:55.330
Sorry!

00:12:56.070 --> 00:12:57.070
Stop it, stop it!

00:13:03.770 --> 00:13:04.950
Can it really be washed off?

00:13:04.950 --> 00:13:05.420
Yes.

00:13:27.940 --> 00:13:28.940
Try this.

00:13:32.390 --> 00:13:33.390
A lip balm?

00:13:33.770 --> 00:13:34.500
Yeah.

00:13:35.470 --> 00:13:36.470
Thanks.

00:13:40.940 --> 00:13:42.540
I have something for you too.

00:13:44.130 --> 00:13:45.130
What is it?

00:13:47.960 --> 00:13:48.960
Give me your hand.

00:13:52.980 --> 00:13:54.990
[Lee Woojin]

00:13:55.220 --> 00:13:56.770
Wow, a basketball!

00:13:56.770 --> 00:13:58.580
[Lee Woojin]

00:13:59.240 --> 00:14:00.240
Thank you.

00:14:01.090 --> 00:14:02.090
It's nothing.

00:14:02.390 --> 00:14:03.390
Don't say that.

00:14:04.020 --> 00:14:06.020
I can't give you anything like this.

00:14:10.340 --> 00:14:12.740
Thanks to you, I had fun today.

00:14:13.500 --> 00:14:14.500
Me too.

00:14:17.520 --> 00:14:18.520
By the way,

00:14:19.150 --> 00:14:20.290
is your hand okay?

00:14:21.270 --> 00:14:22.270
You mean this?

00:14:22.500 --> 00:14:24.060
It's just a minor injury.

00:14:24.220 --> 00:14:26.220
It's not my first time getting hurt.

00:14:26.390 --> 00:14:28.320
Taejun is quite worried about you.

00:14:28.340 --> 00:14:30.380
He's always worried.

00:14:31.640 --> 00:14:33.640
Isn't it because of his good friend?

00:14:34.500 --> 00:14:35.980
We are indeed best friends.

00:14:35.980 --> 00:14:38.110
We've been close since middle school.

00:14:41.210 --> 00:14:43.810
Then why don't you
hang out with him these days?

00:14:45.810 --> 00:14:46.570
Hmm?

00:14:47.420 --> 00:14:49.620
You've been hanging out with me lately.

00:14:51.610 --> 00:14:52.670
That's because...

00:14:55.040 --> 00:14:57.810
it's most fun when being with you
these days.

00:14:58.660 --> 00:15:00.480
I feel happy when I'm with you.

00:15:03.840 --> 00:15:05.640
Am I the only one who thinks that?

00:15:21.800 --> 00:15:22.800
Even if

00:15:22.970 --> 00:15:25.960
you feel bored and unhappy
hanging out with me,

00:15:26.860 --> 00:15:28.720
as long as you don't dislike it,

00:15:30.520 --> 00:15:31.620
don't go anywhere

00:15:31.780 --> 00:15:33.150
and stay with me

00:15:33.870 --> 00:15:35.410
just like you are right now.

00:15:36.950 --> 00:15:38.280
Then I'll make you happy

00:15:38.470 --> 00:15:39.630
and find it fun.

00:15:43.680 --> 00:15:44.680
Got it?

00:16:13.300 --> 00:16:14.010
Let's go.

00:16:52.140 --> 00:16:52.990
Are you okay?

00:16:55.940 --> 00:16:57.240
You can't be with me.

00:16:58.120 --> 00:16:59.100
Hey, what's wrong?

00:16:59.100 --> 00:16:59.740
No.

00:17:01.250 --> 00:17:02.250
I said no.

00:17:07.670 --> 00:17:08.670
Hyeseong!

00:17:09.700 --> 00:17:10.829
Hey, Jang Hyeseong!

00:17:26.619 --> 00:17:27.619
Wow.

00:17:27.780 --> 00:17:29.580
Why was that car driving so fast?

00:17:30.280 --> 00:17:32.010
That could've gone down bad.

00:17:38.720 --> 00:17:39.720
Hyeseong.

00:17:41.370 --> 00:17:41.730
Huh?

00:17:42.100 --> 00:17:42.900
What's wrong?

00:17:45.180 --> 00:17:45.800
Oh...

00:17:45.930 --> 00:17:46.930
Nothing.

00:17:48.700 --> 00:17:50.560
It was really dangerous just now.

00:17:56.370 --> 00:17:57.570
It's the green light.

00:17:59.240 --> 00:18:00.050
Let's go.

00:18:11.050 --> 00:18:13.580
[We almost got into an accident crossing the road.
The same thing happened. What should I do?]

00:18:25.740 --> 00:18:26.070
[Lee Woojin:
I had fun today. See you tomorrow.]

00:18:26.070 --> 00:18:27.070
I had fun today.

00:18:27.390 --> 00:18:28.390
See you tomorrow.

00:18:30.980 --> 00:18:31.050
You're home safely, right?

00:18:31.050 --> 00:18:33.940
[You're home safely, right?]
[Sent]

00:18:33.940 --> 00:18:33.990
[Lee Woojin:
Of course. Good night.]

00:18:33.990 --> 00:18:35.770
Of course.

00:18:36.810 --> 00:18:37.810
Good night.

00:18:54.320 --> 00:18:55.320
From now on,

00:18:55.700 --> 00:18:56.820
I need to keep a distance from him.

00:18:56.820 --> 00:18:57.230
Hey!

00:18:57.260 --> 00:18:58.480
I saw Woojin in person

00:18:58.510 --> 00:18:59.420
yesterday.

00:18:59.430 --> 00:19:00.040
What?

00:19:00.160 --> 00:19:00.960
Gosh.

00:19:01.040 --> 00:19:02.040
I'm so envious.

00:19:02.350 --> 00:19:04.750
I want to see him,
but I haven't been able to.

00:19:04.940 --> 00:19:05.540
How was he?

00:19:05.550 --> 00:19:06.140
Does he really

00:19:06.140 --> 00:19:07.140
shine

00:19:07.150 --> 00:19:07.730
really bright?

00:19:07.730 --> 00:19:08.450
I mean.

00:19:08.510 --> 00:19:09.760
He was so handsome.

00:19:09.960 --> 00:19:11.820
-He's a complete prince charming.
-A complete prince charming?

00:19:11.820 --> 00:19:13.010
-Yes.
-How much so?

00:19:13.050 --> 00:19:14.530
The coolest prince charming on earth.

00:19:14.530 --> 00:19:15.600
The coolest prince charming on earth?

00:19:15.600 --> 00:19:16.680
No—in the universe.

00:19:16.680 --> 00:19:17.680
In the universe?

00:19:19.260 --> 00:19:20.860
The kids' taste nowadays...

00:19:23.960 --> 00:19:24.960
Forget it.

00:19:25.660 --> 00:19:26.660
Hyeseong.

00:19:35.210 --> 00:19:38.470
How about we keep a distance
from each other from tomorrow?

00:19:45.430 --> 00:19:46.180
Okay.

00:19:46.350 --> 00:19:47.350
Just today.

00:20:18.780 --> 00:20:19.780
Hey.

00:20:22.960 --> 00:20:23.960
Oh!

00:20:24.800 --> 00:20:26.530
Why didn't you tell me earlier?

00:20:26.540 --> 00:20:27.400
Hey.

00:20:27.420 --> 00:20:28.940
I just did.

00:20:29.090 --> 00:20:30.820
Why didn't you tell me earlier!

00:20:31.640 --> 00:20:32.350
Hey.

00:20:33.590 --> 00:20:34.130
Let's go.

00:20:41.940 --> 00:20:42.940
What's this?

00:20:43.240 --> 00:20:44.580
Don't you feel uncomfortable?

00:20:44.580 --> 00:20:45.580
Change into this.

00:20:46.540 --> 00:20:47.540
Oh...

00:20:49.720 --> 00:20:50.720
Thanks.

00:21:07.640 --> 00:21:08.320
Here.

00:21:14.540 --> 00:21:15.540
Don't look.

00:21:32.500 --> 00:21:34.310
Don't look. Raise it up.

00:21:38.580 --> 00:21:40.380
Where did you get these clothes?

00:21:40.860 --> 00:21:42.120
I had them just in case.

00:21:42.210 --> 00:21:44.070
I sweat when playing basketball.

00:21:44.600 --> 00:21:45.600
Is your MBTI J?

00:21:46.600 --> 00:21:47.420
J?

00:21:47.800 --> 00:21:48.800
What's that?

00:21:50.230 --> 00:21:50.750
Well...

00:21:51.960 --> 00:21:52.850
Someone who's well-prepared

00:21:52.850 --> 00:21:53.850
is a J...

00:21:54.720 --> 00:21:56.120
What does that even mean?

00:21:57.270 --> 00:21:58.270
I'm done.

00:22:01.880 --> 00:22:02.880
Thanks.

00:22:03.440 --> 00:22:04.570
If you're thankful,

00:22:04.810 --> 00:22:07.070
go to the snack shop and buy me something.

00:22:08.310 --> 00:22:10.240
Why was the car driving so fast?

00:22:10.450 --> 00:22:11.440
[We almost got into an accident crossing the road.
The same thing happened. What should I do?]

00:22:12.510 --> 00:22:13.240
Okay.

00:22:13.430 --> 00:22:14.430
Just one more day.

00:22:18.300 --> 00:22:19.700
Not just the snack store,

00:22:21.940 --> 00:22:23.870
I'll pay for all today's expenses.

00:22:24.190 --> 00:22:25.190
All?

00:22:25.400 --> 00:22:25.970
Yeah.

00:22:29.200 --> 00:22:30.200
Sure.

00:22:46.190 --> 00:22:47.620
-Hello.
-Welcome.

00:23:04.400 --> 00:23:05.650
Thank you.

00:23:05.810 --> 00:23:06.580
Wow.

00:23:06.750 --> 00:23:07.950
This is interesting.

00:23:08.680 --> 00:23:10.880
You've been to a place like this before?

00:23:12.050 --> 00:23:13.500
Order whatever you want.

00:23:13.860 --> 00:23:15.990
It's on me today. Don't feel burdened.

00:23:20.120 --> 00:23:21.550
Bruschetta?

00:23:22.540 --> 00:23:23.540
What's that?

00:23:35.930 --> 00:23:36.930
Are you...

00:23:39.120 --> 00:23:40.320
a second-generation

00:23:40.480 --> 00:23:41.260
chaebol?

00:23:44.230 --> 00:23:45.230
No, I mean,

00:23:46.170 --> 00:23:47.670
I'm a capable adult...

00:23:50.590 --> 00:23:51.990
wannabe.

00:23:52.510 --> 00:23:54.310
It's okay to spend a bit more now.

00:23:56.890 --> 00:23:58.530
Looks like
you're quite confident making it

00:23:58.530 --> 00:23:59.290
as an artist.

00:23:59.790 --> 00:24:00.790
Right?

00:24:01.100 --> 00:24:01.790
Sounds good.

00:24:01.790 --> 00:24:03.110
I'm going to order

00:24:03.130 --> 00:24:03.790
everything I want.

00:24:03.790 --> 00:24:04.790
Sure.

00:24:18.650 --> 00:24:19.650
But it seems like

00:24:20.180 --> 00:24:22.240
this is a place people come for dates.

00:24:23.850 --> 00:24:24.460
Huh?

00:24:25.200 --> 00:24:26.200
We...

00:24:26.780 --> 00:24:28.180
What's next on this date?

00:24:41.530 --> 00:24:42.940
Wow! Wow!

00:24:43.330 --> 00:24:44.130
Gosh.

00:24:44.170 --> 00:24:45.100
Did you see that?

00:24:45.790 --> 00:24:46.390
Amazing.

00:24:47.180 --> 00:24:48.960
Is this really
your first time playing bowling?

00:24:48.960 --> 00:24:49.410
Yeah.

00:24:50.970 --> 00:24:51.970
It's fine.

00:24:52.020 --> 00:24:52.620
Actually,

00:24:53.220 --> 00:24:56.550
I've never been to restaurants
like just now before either.

00:24:57.810 --> 00:24:59.830
I'll teach you how to play.

00:24:59.860 --> 00:25:00.240
Okay.

00:25:06.000 --> 00:25:07.880
Put your hand back.

00:25:12.060 --> 00:25:14.110
Hold the ball like this.

00:25:15.190 --> 00:25:15.960
Hey.

00:25:16.900 --> 00:25:17.900
I'll do it.

00:25:18.310 --> 00:25:19.530
Mine is red, right?

00:25:20.560 --> 00:25:21.180
Yeah.

00:25:22.160 --> 00:25:22.910
Good luck.

00:25:45.710 --> 00:25:46.710
Wow!

00:25:46.740 --> 00:25:48.190
-Amazing!
-Wow!

00:25:48.190 --> 00:25:48.620
Oh.

00:25:48.640 --> 00:25:49.340
I'm sorry.

00:25:52.400 --> 00:25:53.700
-Wow.
-You're good.

00:25:53.910 --> 00:25:54.940
Let me go again.

00:25:59.030 --> 00:26:00.590
Wow, a photobooth.

00:26:04.170 --> 00:26:05.010
Hyeseong.

00:26:05.370 --> 00:26:06.020
Hmm?

00:26:08.740 --> 00:26:10.680
Shall we wear headbands for the photos?

00:26:10.680 --> 00:26:11.680
Huh?

00:26:12.860 --> 00:26:13.860
Wear this.

00:26:14.340 --> 00:26:14.900
Hey.

00:26:15.580 --> 00:26:16.580
I'm wearing this.

00:26:17.610 --> 00:26:19.200
Must I wear it?

00:26:19.710 --> 00:26:21.910
Didn't you say you'd do anything I want?

00:26:22.070 --> 00:26:23.200
Put it on and come in.

00:26:24.390 --> 00:26:25.390
Hurry up.

00:26:26.140 --> 00:26:27.140
Are you serious?

00:26:28.630 --> 00:26:29.630
Come in quickly!

00:26:36.710 --> 00:26:37.970
Okay, I'll listen to you for today.

00:26:37.970 --> 00:26:39.030
I'll listen to you.

00:26:39.550 --> 00:26:40.780
Okay, it's starting.

00:26:40.950 --> 00:26:41.990
What should we do?

00:26:44.750 --> 00:26:46.910
One, two, three.

00:26:48.020 --> 00:26:49.010
Butterfly net.

00:26:49.430 --> 00:26:50.590
Butterfly net?

00:26:52.380 --> 00:26:53.610
One, two, three.

00:27:08.260 --> 00:27:09.820
[We're here!]

00:27:14.020 --> 00:27:15.370
[Hyeseong]

00:27:16.820 --> 00:27:18.220
I'll draw you thick lips.

00:27:18.230 --> 00:27:19.140
Don't!

00:27:19.530 --> 00:27:21.220
Draw it on yourself!

00:27:21.220 --> 00:27:22.530
[Woojin] [Hyeseong]

00:27:22.530 --> 00:27:24.140
[Woojin] [Hyeseong]

00:27:25.220 --> 00:27:26.510
[We're here!]

00:27:32.580 --> 00:27:33.620
Hey, it came out well.

00:27:33.620 --> 00:27:34.670
What's all this?

00:27:34.880 --> 00:27:36.430
-I like this.
-I don't!

00:27:37.950 --> 00:27:39.610
I think this one came out well.

00:27:42.940 --> 00:27:44.210
This is terrible.

00:27:51.860 --> 00:27:53.520
Hey, you spent too much today.

00:27:53.800 --> 00:27:54.800
Let's go dutch.

00:27:55.650 --> 00:27:56.840
What are you talking about?

00:27:56.840 --> 00:27:58.340
I said it's my treat today.

00:27:58.910 --> 00:27:59.790
Is that so?

00:28:00.390 --> 00:28:01.790
I'll treat you next time.

00:28:03.190 --> 00:28:04.190
Gosh.

00:28:05.710 --> 00:28:06.980
I had so much fun today.

00:28:08.250 --> 00:28:09.050
Yeah.

00:28:12.190 --> 00:28:14.090
I've never had so much fun.

00:28:14.990 --> 00:28:15.990
Never?

00:28:16.310 --> 00:28:17.290
Really?

00:28:18.060 --> 00:28:18.600
Yes.

00:28:19.970 --> 00:28:22.770
Because I'd go to art class
every day after school.

00:28:22.820 --> 00:28:23.820
Wow.

00:28:24.440 --> 00:28:26.560
Hey, you'll definitely
get into a fine arts college.

00:28:26.560 --> 00:28:28.240
There's no reason you won't.

00:28:30.950 --> 00:28:33.150
If I do, I will just live my life drawing.

00:28:34.740 --> 00:28:36.470
Is that not the future you want?

00:28:40.270 --> 00:28:41.060
It was.

00:28:42.080 --> 00:28:43.270
Not anymore?

00:28:47.000 --> 00:28:48.940
No, so...

00:28:49.960 --> 00:28:50.690
What's that?

00:28:50.730 --> 00:28:52.160
-So...
-You're drunk.

00:28:52.280 --> 00:28:52.730
Huh?

00:28:53.250 --> 00:28:53.850
Hey!

00:28:54.640 --> 00:28:57.500
That's the art teacher
and the school nurse, right?

00:28:57.750 --> 00:28:58.950
-Right?
-Be careful.

00:29:01.540 --> 00:29:02.170
Hey!

00:29:02.190 --> 00:29:03.190
Hide!

00:29:05.030 --> 00:29:05.610
Why?

00:29:05.620 --> 00:29:06.500
Shh!

00:29:10.430 --> 00:29:11.630
That school nurse...

00:29:12.390 --> 00:29:13.390
